ination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Baynard was born about 1292, in Norfolk, England, United Kingdom as the son of Robert Baynard. He died about 1329, in his hometown, at the age of 39."},"et":{"Abt 1292–Abt 1329":"umbes 1292–umbes 1329","1292–1329":"1292–1329","1286–1330":"1286–1330","1300–Female":"1300–Surnud","1289–1331":"1289–1331","1220–1299":"1220–1299","1289":"1289","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1331":"1331","1220":"1220","1330":"1330","1286":"1286","Abt 1292":"umbes 1292","Abt 1329":"umbes 1329","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1292–Abt 1329":"noin 1292–noin 1329","1292–1329":"1292–1329","1286–1330":"1286–1330","1300–Female":"1300–Kuollut","1289–1331":"1289–1331","1220–1299":"1220–1299","1289":"1289","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1331":"1331","1220":"1220","1330":"1330","1286":"1286","Abt 1292":"noin 1292","Abt 1329":"noin 1329","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1292–Abt 1329":"environ 1292–environ 1329","1292–1329":"1292–1329","1286–1330":"1286–1330","1300–Female":"1300–Décédée","1289–1331":"1289–1331","1220–1299":"1220–1299","1289":"1289","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1331":"1331","1220":"1220","1330":"1330","1286":"1286","Abt 1292":"environ 1292","Abt 1329":"environ 1329","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert Baynard est né environ 1292, à Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Robert Baynard. Il est décédé environ 1329, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 39 ans."},"de":{"Abt 1292–Abt 1329":"um 1292–um 1329","1292–1329":"1292–1329","1286–1330":"1286–1330","1300–Female":"1300–Verstorben","1289–1331":"1289–1331","1220–1299":"1220–1299","1289":"1289","1300":"1300","1299":"1299